                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i><span>4.89</span><span>(47)</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-certificate"></i><span>Superhost</span>
                            <p>location</p>
                            <div class="currency">$250CAD/peron & night</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="desc">
                            <hr>
                            <div class="headTitle">Party House</div>
                            <div class="detail">The Crooked Cottage is a newly renovated farmhouse in the heart of
                                Niagara wine country. There are hundreds of trees surrounding this quiet space. The name
                                is self explanatory as you will have a few chuckles as you explore the crookedness of
                                this cute space:). There is a private spot to have backyard fires and we provide you
                                with brochures and a wall wine map so you can explore the beauty of wine country.

                                Private exterior entrance and coin operated laundry facility located onsite at North
                                Creek.</div>
                            <hr>
                            <div class="amenity">Amenities</div>
                            <div class="detail">
                                <i class="fas fa-fire"></i>
                                Indoor fireplace
                                <br>
                                <i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i>
                                Hangers
                                <br>
                                <i class="fas fa-play"></i>
                                Pack â€™n Play/travel crib
                                <br>
                                <i class="fas fa-parking"></i>
                                Free parking on premises
                                <br>
                                <i class="fas fa-wifi"></i>
                                Wifi
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="booking">
                        <form class="user-form">
                            <!-- action="/aboutUs" method="get"-->
                            <div class="head">
                                <p>Book Now</p>
                                <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i>
                            </div>
                            <hr>
                            <div class="input checkIn">
                                <p>Check-In</p>
                                <input required type="datetime-local" id="date-in" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="input checkOut">
                                <p>Check-Out</p>
                                <input required type="datetime-local" id="date-out" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="input checkOut">
                                <p>Number of Guests</p>
                                <input type="number" id="quantity" name="quantity" value="0">
                                <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="input">
                                <div class="head">
                                    <p>Total</p>
                                </div>
                                <p>$CAD</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="reserve">
                                <input type="submit" id="reserve" value="Reserve Now" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="reset">
                                <input type="reset" id="reset" value="Reset" />
                            </div>
                            <br />
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>

        </section>
    </main>
    <hr class="line">
    </hr>
    <footer>
    </footer>
